                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote scope="sole" xml:id="hand-1">
                                <p>The text was copied in a <term type="script">mixed
                                    minuscule</term> script, slanting slightly to the right, in
                                    brown ink, with modest variation in letter size.</p>
                                <p>Syllabic abbreviations and superscript word endings do not
                                    appear. Breathings are angular and mute <hi rend="italic">iota</hi> is adscript. <foreign xml:lang="la">Nomina
                                            sacra</foreign> two letters long are unaccentuated.</p>
                                <p>Punctuation used includes the middle and upper points and
                                    question mark.</p>
                            </handNote>
                        </handDesc>
                        
                        <additions>Some corrections have been noted in the margin. The fragment has
                            been marked with the present classmark and the former classmark
                            T.14.</additions>
